<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.6.10">
<l>ētamvan taṇukā vaṇṇanā meṇṇi</l>
<l>yeḻumiṉō toḻutumeṉ ṟimaiyōr</l>
<l>nātaṉvan tiṟaiñcum naimicā raṇiyat</l>
<l>tentaiyaic cintaiyuḷ vaittu</l>
<l>kātalē mikutta kaliyaṉvā yōlicey</l>
<l>mālaitām kaṟṟuval lārka</l>
<l>ḷōtanīr vaiyaka māṇṭuveṇ kuṭaikkī</l>
<l>ḻumparu mākuvar tāmē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who master learning the garland composed of the poems</l>
<l rend="indent">by Kaliyaṉ, whose love abounds,</l>
<l>Keeping in his thoughts our father in Naimiśāraṇyam</l>
<l rend="indent">where the lord of celestials arrives and bows,</l>
<l>Saying, “Oh, arise; we will worship [here] contemplating a way that suffering</l>
<l rend="indent">may not come and advance (upon us),”</l>
<l>Having ruled the earth, with its flooding seas, under a white umbrella,</l>
<l rend="indent">they will also become celestials.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
